attr.title: Retro Highway
attr.desc:
Return to the days of pure arcade fun!  
Retro Highway is a throwback racing game aiming to combine the accessibility of modern titles with the high-skill challenge and charming aesthetics of old.
attr.inst:
Purchase the game from Itch.io.
Download the Windows version and place RetroHighway.zip in ports/retrohighway/assets
attr.inst_md:
Purchase the game from [Itch.io](https://nicolaigd.itch.io/retro-highway).
